snippet.title: GRANDIA HD Collection - PlayStation & Xbox Trailer
snippet.description:
The GRANDIA HD Collection launches on PlayStation & Xbox platforms on 3/26! Get your hands on two games that changed the landscape of RPGs forever, now in stunning HD.

For more information, check out:
Official Website: https://bit.ly/GrandiaHD
